  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the use of negative pleural suction in
      tube thoracostomy is more effective than water seal alone for the treatment of pneumothorax
      and/or hemothorax in patients with chest trauma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
